    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Shoes intended as streetwear for women or girls that have a deep instep opening, and that are derived stylistically from ballet slippers. These feature a sturdier leather or plastic sole and typically have no heel or a very low one.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
